<title>yạlly btḥbny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - yạlly btḥbny ... yạlly gẖmrtny yạlly dkẖlt qlby wjyt nwrtny ḥyạty ạtgẖyrt ... wqywdy ạ̹tksrt
 wạlṣʿbh mʿạk btʿdy wmn ywmhạ mạ sbtny̱
 1- hfḍl ṭwl ʿmry fạkr ... ạ̹n ạlhy qạdr
 ạ̉qwy̱ mn
 kl ẓrwfy, wyạh mfy
 sẖ
 mstḥyl wạ̹n ṣlạty sạmʿ ... lw fy msẖklh wạqʿ
 bkrh ạlfjr ṭạlʿ mhmạ ṭạl ạllyl
 2- ạnạ qlby bḥbh dạyb mn ywm mạjtlh tạyb
 dẗ ạlly ydwr ʿlyh, bylạqy f ḥḍnh mkạn
 hw byrḥm dmwʿnạ mstny ywm rjwʿnạ
 msẖ hydkẖl qlwbnạ mn
 gẖyr ạ̉stạ̉dẖạn</lyrics>
